headline: Lululemon, Samsara Eco Deepen Partnership For Recycled Materials, Targets Circularity by 2030
summary: Lululemon Athletica Inc. (NASDAQ:LULU) is one of the best Canadian stocks with huge upside potential. On June 11, Lululemon announced an expanded 10-year partnership with Samsara Eco through an off-take agreement for recycled nylon and polyester.
